&lt;li&gt;Guide and perform financial analyses that help in the evaluation of strategic options, including financial outlook, NPV, and scenario/sensitivity analysis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate findings/recommendations with management and support business collaboration discussions with key stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with other departments and help support the annual strategic planning process and execution/implementation plans.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive project-based strategic initiatives end-to-end from problem definition and project scoping to delivery of recommendations to the executive team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work cross-functionally, including building consensus and influencing decision making.&lt;/li&gt;
